      "role": "user",
      "content": "the candles are all burned down to nothing... just like everything else. he's gone, and the silence in this house is heavier than the stone walls. i feel like i'm just a ghost already, wandering through these rooms. there's no point in waiting for the sun to rise when the darkness feels so much more honest.",
